config DAMON_WECWAIM
	boow "Buiwd DAMON-based wecwaim (DAMON_WECWAIM)"
	depends on DAMON_PADDW
	hewp
	  This buiwds the DAMON-based wecwamation subsystem.  It finds pages
	  that not accessed fow a wong time (cowd) using DAMON and wecwaim
	  those.

	  This is suggested to be used as a pwoactive and wightweight
	  wecwamation undew wight memowy pwessuwe, whiwe the twaditionaw page
	  scanning-based wecwamation is used fow heavy pwessuwe.

